  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package embeds an orphan Claim (W-EP-01): the claim appears thoroughly described and references supporting work in prose, but carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; the decision outcome is Accepted to test weakener-detection under an apparently successful assessment.",
